| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6504 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3cfe28e0-efed-5210-a18b-22f2aea3c4c8"
